&lt;div id="gamejam-project-smile-or-perish" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#gamejam-project-smile-or-perish" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>This was a GameJam project at Poznan University of Technology, combining machine learning with Unity. The premise of the game is simple: the player lives in a world where the political doctrine forbids showing negative emotions. The player&amp;rsquo;s task is to smile at the right moments—literally smile. The game incorporates OpenSeeFace for facial tracking using a webcam, integrated with the gameplay.
&lt;a href="https://globalgamejam.org/games/2024/happy-dictatorship-4-0" target="_blank">GameLink&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="/gamejam-projects/1727631161834-happy-dictatorship/featured.png"/></item><item><title>Suppliers</title><link>/gamejam-projects/1727631754977-suppliers/</link><pubDate>Mon, 08 Aug 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/gamejam-projects/1727631754977-suppliers/</guid><description>&lt;h2 class="relative group">Suppliers: A United with Ukraine Game Jam Project
